Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The most precious moment in life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is the time of decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but it also leaves us with many lessons to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ketsudan = (decision)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your wisdom. Use your head Keep thinking if you're a man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you cry or laugh, it depends on your decision
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be arrogant even if you win Don't cry even if you lose
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Man does not show tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsunoko Production
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,December 2nd, 1941, five days before the surprise attack at Pearl Harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The great fortress of Singapore, pride of Britain, was full of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because the battleship Prince of Wales and the battle cruiser Repulse arrived at the port as the new main force of the British East Indies Fleet: Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This was announced worldwide, and no one doubted that Singapore's defense was an iron wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sinking of the Prince of Wales and Repulse (Episode Seven)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Wales is a state-of-the-art battleship called the "Unsinkable Battleship"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because it never succumbed to the attack of the German battleship Bismarck in the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,35,000 tons, max speed 28.3 knots,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,armed with 10, 35 cm cannons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and 16, 13 cm high angle cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The eight-armed anti-aircraft guns, called "pom-pom guns", fired 6,000 shots per minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She is also equipped with a number of dual cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Battlecruiser Repulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,32,000 tons, max speed 30 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned as she was her equipment was almost the same as the Prince of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Japanese military Hainan Island base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales and Repulse are at Singapore Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.48,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we sortie, they will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We must make our landing a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no guarantee that we will be able to hide ourselves from the enemy and land.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the British East Indies Fleet exists, it will be dangerous to supply the Army from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to destroy the British fleet as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales and Repulse will be destroyed by our Air Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, I leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:04:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I am prepared to safely deliver the landing party even if my escort fleet is wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will definitely protect our fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When they come out, be sure to hit them from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sunrise is Yamagata". This encrypted telegram announced the decision to open the war on December 8th,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Japanese troops secretly advanced toward the Malay Peninsula and Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Above the fleet. One British aircraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They are finally coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy will be sending telegrams such as "Discovered the Japanese Navy's Grand Fleet" by this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if the British East Indies Fleet came out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind. If the Prince of Wales comes out, it will be in the sea west of the Anambas Islands, where mines have already been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If they mistakenly come from the east, they will only find the eyes of our submarines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if the British realize the purpose of the surprise landing, it will hinder the entire Maylayan campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As planned, the course will be north-northwest and we will be shown to be heading for Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese fleet is heading for Bangkok, with 25 transport ships, one battleship, five cruisers, and seven destroyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Air Force General Brooke-Popham General Commander of the British Far East force in Singapore,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,did not take any measures because the purpose of the Japanese fleet was still unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese convoy suddenly changed course to the west at 00:45 on the 8th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them have begun landing on parts of the Malay Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon on receiving this information, Phillips, Commander-in-Chief of the British East Indies Fleet, gathered his staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The only target of the Japanese army that landed last night, is Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible for the Japanese army to bring Singapore down from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The British Force Z will make a surprise attack
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with the support of the Air Force
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the Japanese fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 20 warships escorting the Japanese fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole world knows that Prince of Wales and Repulse are in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We are no longer hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever we meet an enemy, we fight and hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pride and tradition of our Royal Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,5:35 p.m. on the 8th. Force Z of the British East Indies Fleet, whose flagship is Prince of Wales,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,has set sail from Singapore's military port to launch a surprise attack on the Japanese fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a telegraph from the Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My fighters are heavily damaged by the Japanese force, and it is impossible to escort Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's make a surprise attack without the the Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go around the east side of the Anambas Islands and proceed north.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese know that if we pass, it will be on the west side. It's impassable if mines are set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Force Z safely avoided a swarm of mines on the west side of the Anambas Islands and moved north.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, on the afternoon of the 9th, Force Z was completely unaware that a Japanese submarine was waiting in its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.12,0:08:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The telegraph of the discovery of Force Z was sent to the base of the 22nd Japanese Air Squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency telegraph has been sent from the 5th Submarine Squadron, the 30th Submersible, I-65.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw two enemy Repulse-type battlecruisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Course 340°, speed 14 knots, 1515.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales and Repulse have just been seen by our reconnaissance planes this morning when they were in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, which one is correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Develop the reconnaissance photos. It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a large merchant ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is neither the Prince of Wales nor Repulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If so what about the telegraph from I-65?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can trust it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is heading here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At 5:34 p.m., torpedo bombers were launched from the air bases in Saigon and Tudomo for an attack on Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japanese convoy on the eastern side of the Malay Peninsula immediately retreated to the coast of Thailand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and the heavy cruiser and other escort ships proceeded to destroy Britain's Force Z in cooperation with the aviation unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no regrets if we fight against Prince of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop them from getting closer until the entire fleet of troops has landed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It is impossible in this storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I turn back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At 8:10 p.m., the torpedo bombers that took of from the Tsudomo base discovered a fleet that looked like Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Discovered enemy ships. 150°, 140 km
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They mistook our ships for the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It you do not contact them quickly, we will be attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately send a telegraph. "We are the allies who are illuminated."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconnaissance is impossible due to bad weather. There is also a chance of mistaking friendly ships for enemy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Return the attack force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We will try again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, the British fleet thought they were found by the Japanese side, and they quickly turned back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.16,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Japanese side did not discover Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,both the enemies and the friendlies turned their backs at the same time and parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:13:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Force Z, who abandoned the surprise attack, is returning to Singapore at 00:52 on the 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, an emergency call from the Singapore headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It says that the Japanese army is landing on Kuantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you can make a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, 640 km from the Japanese military base in Saigon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, there is no need to worry about being attacked by Japanese aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can crush the enemy convoy and escort the fleet at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I can do it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let one destroyer scout ahead first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Force Z sent the destroyer Express to Kuantan first,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and started advancing with the hope of ambushing the Japanese fleet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,although Force Z was completely unaware,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Its actions were discovered by the Japanese submarine I-58.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Never let it go this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoroughly find out the movement of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find them, hit them with the whole force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sink Prince of Wales and Repulse by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can definitely do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately send the reconnaissance aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At 4:55 a.m., nine Mitsubishi G3M planes took off for reconnaissance from Saigon base.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Japanese side was still searching for British Force Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did the Royal Navy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have passed the planned 600 nautical miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we can go home as it is? We looked for them thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see the Malay Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's Kuantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, a shadow was reflected in the captain's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.88,0:15:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the clouds to get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It is definitely Prince of Wales and Repulse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the telegram
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Discovered Prince of Wales. 4° north latitude, 3° 55' east longitude, 60° course.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They are shooting at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we brought a torpedo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconnaissance is boring
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,War cannot be done alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconnaissance and sinking enemy ships are the same mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on them until our attack aircraft arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The third reconnaissance aircraft discovered the enemy's main force off the coast of Kuantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let it escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,be sure to sink it by plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Every attack aircraft is rushing to Kuantan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese attack aircraft will definitely come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales is not afraid of airplane attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is also desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure the counterattack plan is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to attack at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to show the bravery of the Royal Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock all enemy planes into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy main force, change of direction. Course 60°, speed 20 knots.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the attacking unit doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone. Throw away your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is to save fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons and clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, eight Japanese air squadrons reached 3,000 meters above Repulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.24,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time in naval history, the battle of airplane vs battleship began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A bomb hit the Repulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't sink in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the torpedo bomber unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two torpedoes hit the Prince of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The engines have stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight until the last soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Telegraph to Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are being bombed by the Japanese Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is also doing a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, it is an unsinkable battleship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighth company with eight aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle of the British fleet was tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the end came to the Repulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your life jackets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on your life jackets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew gather on the upper deck and prepare to leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,God save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Repulse is sinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. She fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Prince of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.30,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All crew have left the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She fought well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.68,0:21:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the knight of the British Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, let's go to the lifeboats right away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince of Wales is sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.10,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there is not enough fuel to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Report the results of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they out of bullets?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, its Bushido.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.62,0:22:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An unsinkable battleship was sunk by airplane.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The successful capture of Singapore is only a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, a Japanese plane flew to the sinking site of Prince of Wales and Repulse to drop two bouquets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle between the Japanese and British forces in the Naval Battle of Malaya was spectacular and imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One bouquet is for the British soldiers and the other is for the Japanese soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These were for their devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.28,0:23:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight to fulfill their mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.14,0:23:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the Japanese Navy did not fully asses the arrival of the aviation era, and eventually went on the road to a major defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pacific War taught us the preciousness of peace, but it also leaves us with many lessons to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.49,0:24:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Battle of the Coral Sea (Episode Eight)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.84,0:24:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a man, test your strength If you are a man, burn your hope
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.44,0:24:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you area man, don't let yourself down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.92,0:25:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I and you are men and men bleed the same bright red blood.
